name: 朱莉娅-安布拉·维莱恩
name_full: 朱莉娅-安布拉·维莱恩 Julia-Ambra Verlaine

last_movies.title: 散户大战华尔街：游戏驿站传奇

introduction: Julia-Ambra Verlaine writes about financial markets for The Wall Street Journal in New York. She previously covered financial services and regulation in the European Union for the Journal's bureau in Brussels. Ms. Verlaine also reported on the investment banking sector in London for Bloomberg News.
